text: Inbiocystiscus is a genus of minute sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusc in the family Cystiscidae. == Species== Species within the genus Inbiocystiscus include: *Inbiocystiscus faroi Ortea & Espinosa, 2006 *Inbiocystiscus gamezi Ortea & Espinosa, 2001 *Inbiocystiscus tanialeonae Ortea & Espinosa, 2016 *Inbiocystiscus triplicatus Espinosa & Ortea, 2007 == References == Category:Cystiscidae
title: Inbiocystiscus
